General.Name: Impact Coatings publ AB
General.Description: Impact Coatings AB (publ) engages in the development and commercialization of physical vapor deposition (PVD) surface treatment solutions in Sweden. The company offers INLINECOATER PVD coating systems; and provides coating, support, maintenance, and spare parts services. Impact Coatings AB (publ) was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Linköping, Sweden.
